text: Henk Lotgering (11 February 1903 - 13 September 1984) was a Dutch diver. He competed at the 1924 Summer Olympics and the 1928 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1903 births Category:1984 deaths Category:Dutch male divers Category:Olympic divers of the Netherlands Category:Divers at the 1924 Summer Olympics Category:Divers at the 1928 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Amsterdam
